                                        2009,
                                        2261,
                                        2656
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " to imitate different perspectives of a single image. The relevance module uses a scoring mechanism to weigh the retrieved open- world knowledge and image features to ensure the most relevant information and combine them for final prediction."
